        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Ephesians",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", p. 281) gives several examples from papyri of similar formulas of closing, especially two, which read, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
